Bring 2 cups water to boil in saucepan. Stir in noodles. Reduce heat to medium-low; cover. Simmer 8 minutes or until noodles are tender. Do not drain. Add VELVEETA, vegetables, tuna and pepper; stir until VELVEETA is melted. Try serving with whole wheat rolls and a quick bagged salad tossed with your favorite KRAFT Dressing such as Ranch.